          <h2>
           <a id="training">
           </a>
           Upcoming Training Modules
          </h2>
          <p>
           Are you interested in learning about issues around diversity? Attend our training
                                 modules to learn more about issues of diversity in a safe environment, which will
                                 be essential to better serve our ever changing student population. Please note, the
                                 modules must be taken sequentially.
          </p>
          <div class="scroll-overflow-sm">
           <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
