               </strong>
              </td>
             </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
             <tr>
              <td>
               Tue., April 2
              </td>
              <td>
               <span>
                Module 1 -
               </span>
               <span>
                Exploring Self &amp; Others
               </span>
              </td>
              <td>
               <span>
                Union Pano East
               </span>
              </td>
              <td>
               <span>
                1-3pm
               </span>
              </td>
             </tr>
             <tr>
              <td>
               Wed., April 24
              </td>
              <td>
               <span>
                Module 2 - Exploring Power, Bias, &amp; Values
               </span>
              </td>
              <td>
               CPDC Library in 350 SSB
              </td>
              <td>
               10am-12pm
              </td>
             </tr>
             <tr>
              <td>
               Wed., April 24
              </td>
              <td>
               <span>
                Module 3 - Putting it all Together: Dialoging About Social Justice
               </span>
              </td>
              <td>
               <span>
                CPDC Library in 350 SSB
               </span>
              </td>
              <td>
               1-3pm
              </td>
             </tr>
            </tbody>
           </table>
          </div>
          <p>
           <span>
            If you are trying to register within three days of the training, please register by
                                    emailing Olivia Harker
           </span>
           <span style="line-height: 1.75;">
            (
            <a href="mailto:OHarker@sa.utah.edu?subject=SADC%20Training%20Question">
             OHarker@sa.utah.edu
            </a>
           </span>
